The paper discusses the development of deep learning models for click-through rate prediction, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). It also involves the use of user behavior data and recommender systems, which are related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of image data in online advertising, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the use of deep learning models for user interest modeling, which is a common application of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
